divs: sighting detailssighting report: i have two photographs taken just seconds apart. it was just before dark. #37 was taken on tuesday 10\05\2004 at 9:58:55pm. picture #38 was also taken on tuesday 10\05\2004 but at 9:58:56pm. now, at the time when i took these shots it was all about the sunset. a few months ago i decided to use one of these photos for my comuter desktop, i look at it everyday. i don t know what was different tonight but i saw a little speck on the screen that didn t seem right. so, i went to retrieve the shot from it s file. i noticed that there were two "specks" not one. i tried to zoom in on them but it gets too distorted. however, the strangest thing about this is... it s not my first sighting. my first sighting was nine or ten years ago, i reported that sighting as well. but, even stranger than that is,the ufo s in these photos, look exactly like the one i saw years ago. also, these sightings are within maybe one mile of each other. so, check that out! good luck, i can t wait to hear from you.
